 =NOWnews 今日新聞網|accessdate =2011-03-30|archive-date =2011-12-26|archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20111226132827/http://www.nownews.com/2011/03/30/138-2701048.htm|dead-url =no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|language =zh-tw|url =http://www.bcc.com.tw/news/newsview.asp?cde=1451156|title =粉妹霸凌案 兩名康叔落網另一自首 與黑道無關|publisher =中廣新聞|accessdate =2011-03-30}}{{dead link|date=2018年3月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite news|language =zh-tw|url =http://tw.nextmedia.com/rnews/article/SecID/102/art_id/22201/IssueID/20110330|title =扮黑道「康叔」挺象腿幫　2生到案臉發白|publisher =蘋果日報|accessdate =2011-03-29|archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20110402065753/http://tw.nextmedia.com/rnews/article/SecID/102/art_id/22201/IssueID/20110330|archive-date =2011-04-02|dead-url =yes}}</ref>。參與打人的七名少女採尿液檢體調查是否涉毒，送驗結果3月30日下午出爐，七名少女檢體皆呈陰性反應<ref>{{cite news|language=zh-tw|url=http://udn.com/NEWS/SOCIETY/BREAKINGNEWS2/6244251.shtml|title =霸凌案打人7少女 驗尿呈陰性反應|publisher =聯合報|accessdate =2011-03-30}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|language =zh-tw|url =http://tw.nextmedia.com/rnews/article/SecID/102/art_id/22299/IssueID/20110330/page/1|title =象腿幫7少女 驗尿呈陰性未涉毒|publisher =蘋果日報|accessdate =2011-03-30}}{{Dead link|date=2020年1月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>。

